    \noindent
    Thank you first and foremost to my supervisor, Yvette Perrott, for your continued guidance and encouragement throughout this thesis. Without your patience and ability to clarify the many questions I had, this thesis would not have been possible.

    Thank you to my family and friends for their unwavering support throughout my Master's degree, and for patiently listening to discussions about my research.

    I thank the administrative staff of the Raapoi High Performance Cluster at Victoria University of Wellington for their technical support, and the NRAO Science Helpdesk for their assistance with \textit{CASA}-related queries.

    Artificial intelligence tools, ChatGPT (OpenAI, versions 4o, 5.1, and 5.2), were utilised in a supportive capacity over the course of this thesis. Assistance was provided in generation of code templates, plot styling, background research and concept clarification, and proofreading for understanding and flow.
    These tools were not used for any analysis of data, formation of conclusions, or writing sections of the thesis. All scientific results, conclusions, and final edits are the author's own work.
